		<title>小狗遭棄養差點安樂死！救援志工不忍決定給牠一個新家 </title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/10/02/%e5%b0%8f%e7%8b%97%e9%81%ad%e6%a3%84%e9%a4%8a%e5%b7%ae%e9%bb%9e%e5%ae%89%e6%a8%82%e6%ad%bb%ef%bc%81%e6%95%91%e6%8f%b4%e5%bf%97%e5%b7%a5%e4%b8%8d%e5%bf%8d%e6%b1%ba%e5%ae%9a%e7%b5%a6%e7%89%a0%e4%b8%80/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 洪瑜蓉]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Thu, 02 Oct 2025 06:34:52 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[新寵]]></category>
