		<title>狗狗躲在籠子不出來怎麼辦？恐是這「5種」心理問題作祟</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/10/02/%e7%8b%97%e7%8b%97%e8%ba%b2%e5%9c%a8%e7%b1%a0%e5%ad%90%e4%b8%8d%e5%87%ba%e4%be%86%e6%80%8e%e9%ba%bc%e8%be%a6%ef%bc%9f%e6%81%90%e6%98%af%e9%80%99%e3%80%8c5%e7%a8%ae%e3%80%8d%e5%bf%83%e7%90%86%e5%95%8f/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 時事新聞]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Thu, 02 Oct 2025 05:43:28 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[新寵]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[時事]]></category>
